Exception::Class
Exporter
File::Temp
File::Basename
Getopt::Long
IPC::Cmd
List::MoreUtils
Pod::Usage
Readonly
Scalar::Util
Statistics::Descriptive
Test::Exception
Test::More
Test::Pod
Test::Pod::Coverage
Test::Warn
version


